            <h2>Best time to visit Auckland</h2>
            <p class="text-justify">The best time to visit Auckland is during the summer season of New Zealand, ideally between December and the beginning of March. Auckland's natural beauty is more appealing during summers, and all outdoor activities are best experienced when it is sunny and warm. You can also enjoy and explore many music and art festivals during summertime. </p>

            <p class="text-justify">Some festivals are Wonder Garden, St. Jerome's Laneway Festival, and Splore. Every year in January, Auckland's version of Wimbledon takes place at the ASB Classic tennis tournament. The months mentioned above offer pleasant temperatures, mostly sunny days and thin tourist crowds. Hence you can explore Auckland to the fullest. </p>

